        {
            "title": "英特爾與Google AI合作推動下 週漲幅擴大至逾33%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英特爾\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英特爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英特爾\">英特爾</a>公司(NASDAQ:INTC)週四上漲1%,延續漲勢,過去五個交易日股價飆升33%,這家晶片製造商正成為AI<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"基礎設施\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:基礎設施;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/基礎設施\">基礎設施</a>建設的焦點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾宣布與Google達成多年期合作協議,共同推進AI和雲端基礎設施發展,股價隨之攀升。此次合作聚焦於<span><span><span><span>英特爾</span></span></span></span> Xeon處理器和客製化基礎設施處理單元(IPU),旨在提升Google全球營運的效率和性能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據協議,Google Cloud將繼續在其工作負載優化實例中部署英特爾Xeon處理器,包括為C4和N4實例提供動力的最新英特爾Xeon 6處理器。這些平台支援從大規模AI訓練協調到延遲敏感型推理及通用運算等各類工作負載。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f9bc908f-8d98-365c-a501-95dcfe72a535-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾和Google還將擴大客製化ASIC基礎IPU的共同開發。這些可程式化加速器可將網路、儲存和安全功能從主機CPU卸載,提高利用率,並在超大規模AI環境中實現更可預測的性能表現。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾執行長譚立武(Lip-Bu Tan)表示:「AI正在重塑基礎設施的建構和擴展方式。擴展AI不僅需要加速器,更需要平衡的系統。CPU和IPU是提供現代AI工作負載所需性能、效率和靈活性的核心。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Google AI基礎設施首席技術官兼高級副總裁Amin Vahdat表示,英特爾近二十年來一直是值得信賴的合作夥伴,其Xeon路線圖讓他們有信心滿足日益增長的性能和效率需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週稍早,英特爾與SpaceX、xAI和特斯拉一同加入Terafab晶片生產專案後,漲勢進一步加速。有消息稱英特爾於週末接待了馬斯克(Elon Musk),並確認參與該合作計畫,股價隨之上揚。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Lynx Equity分析師KC Rajkumar最近指出,英特爾在解決客戶晶圓供應問題方面取得進展,該問題曾導致三個月前發布的第一季度業績指引低於季節性水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E8%88%87google-ai%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8B-%E9%80%B1%E6%BC%B2%E5%B9%85%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE33-142539131.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 23:01:38",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "台新元富證合併後APP異常 金管會：已通報重大偶發 責成證交所查核",
